-- ############################################################################
-- SUMMARY
-- ############################################################################
--
-- This file demonstrates:
--
-- ENUMERATIONS (Level 1)
--   - Basic enumerations: IDENTIFIER 'Caption'
--   - Inline documentation for enum values
--
-- DATA TYPES (Level 2)
--   - String(length), Integer, Long, Decimal, Boolean
--   - DateTime, Date, AutoNumber, Binary
--   - Enumeration(Module.Enum)
--
-- CONSTRAINTS (Level 3)
--   - NOT NULL ERROR 'message'
--   - UNIQUE ERROR 'message'
--   - DEFAULT value
--
-- INDEXES (Level 4)
--   - Single column: INDEX (Column)
--   - Composite: INDEX (Col1, Col2)
--   - With direction: INDEX (Column ASC/DESC)
--
-- DOCUMENTATION (Level 5)
--   - Entity JavaDoc: /** ... */
--   - Inline attribute docs
--   - @see references
--
-- ASSOCIATIONS (Level 6)
--   - Reference (Many-to-One)
--   - ReferenceSet (Many-to-Many)
--   - Self-referencing (Hierarchical)
--   - DELETE_BEHAVIOR options
--
-- VIEW ENTITIES (Level 7)
--   - SELECT with aliases
--   - Aggregations (COUNT, SUM, AVG)
--   - JOINs via association path
--   - WHERE and GROUP BY
--
-- NON-PERSISTENT ENTITIES (Level 8)
--   - Search parameters
--   - API responses
--   - Dashboard metrics
--
-- CREATE OR MODIFY (Level 9)
--   - Idempotent entity creation/modification
--   - @RenamedFrom('oldName') for attribute renaming
--   - Compatible type changes (widening)
--   - Works with PERSISTENT, NON-PERSISTENT, and VIEW
--
-- ALTER ENTITY (Level 10)
--   - ADD ATTRIBUTE with types and constraints
--   - RENAME ATTRIBUTE for non-destructive renames
--   - MODIFY ATTRIBUTE for type changes (e.g., widen string)
--   - DROP ATTRIBUTE to remove fields
--   - SET DOCUMENTATION / SET COMMENT for metadata
--   - ADD INDEX / DROP INDEX for performance tuning
--   - Combined multi-action statements
--   - Quoted identifiers for reserved-word attribute names ("Range", `Order`)
--
-- ENTITY GENERALIZATION (Level 12)
--   - EXTENDS System.FileDocument for file storage
--   - EXTENDS System.Image for image entities
--   - EXTENDS application entities (type hierarchies)
--   - EXTENDS with no additional attributes
--   - GENERALIZATION keyword (legacy syntax)
--   - CREATE OR MODIFY with EXTENDS
--   - Associations to generalized entities
--
-- Total: 45+ domain model elements
--
-- ############################################################################
